title: Late
html: It’s 11:41pm. I did get some work done today, and I had a meeting. I went for a drive and got food from a milk tea place near me. I also finished up my taxes; I think I received my last forms today, but I’ll wait a bit in case I get anything else.

relatedPosts.title: Assembly
relatedPosts.html: Last week I was assembling a bunch of furniture. I like doing that. I almost took a job doing it after college. Driving around in a van assembling people’s ikea shelves. That would’ve been fun.
